1
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,000
"Candy"

2
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:46,200
(Episode 4: Your Scent Hasn't Changed)

3
00:01:25,239 --> 00:01:26,239
Xiao He.

4
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,519
It's so nice to have you by my side.

5
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:40,560
Wen Nuannuan...

6
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:41,959
Hold it right there.

7
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,560
Did you forget you were just mad at her?

8
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,200
Lin Can.

9
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,799
Don't leave me.

10
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:50,879
Lin Can.

11
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,199
Did you...

12
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,599
make all of this?

13
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,000
Of course.

14
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,120
A love-filled breakfast.

15
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:57,599
It sure is...

16
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:00,039
What?

17
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:01,439
Got a problem?

18
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,479
No, no, no.

19
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,039
I'll do the cooking from now on.

20
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:06,960
Fine.

21
00:03:07,319 --> 00:03:08,319
You said it yourself.

22
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:12,919
I did.

23
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,759
How about we eat this instead today?

24
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:18,439
Here.

25
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:24,439
Did you sleep well last night?

26
00:03:25,319 --> 00:03:26,439
I'll take the couch tonight.

27
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:30,400
But last night...

28
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,639
things were fine.

29
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,759
Why take the couch today?

30
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,360
Yesterday was yesterday.

31
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,560
Today is today.

32
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:43,360
I need to return Si Han's call.

33
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:45,599
You're afraid Sister Si Han
will misunderstand, right?

34
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:49,280
Afraid she'll get jealous...

35
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,720
if she knows we slept together?

36
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,000
You really want to know?

37
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,479
Actually, yesterday...

38
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:04,800
When did you...

39
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:08,479
start liking Sister Si Han?

40
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,919
You big jerk!

41
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,800
Get away from me!

42
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:20,439
I don't want you anymore!

43
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,000
Understand now?

44
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:44,000
Why didn't you say so earlier?!

45
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:47,120
You look pretty cute when you're jealous.

46
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:51,480
Si Han and I...

47
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,480
are just good friends.

48
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,800
Nothing more.

49
00:04:56,519 --> 00:04:57,719
Anything else you want to ask?

50
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,800
Well...

51
00:05:02,117 --> 00:05:03,310
(Si Han calling)

52
00:05:04,117 --> 00:05:05,117
Hello?

53
00:05:05,278 --> 00:05:06,278
Hello?

54
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:06,879
Lin Can.

55
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,359
Got some good news for you.

56
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,999
There's a countryside reality show...

57
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,440
that wants you as its lead guest.

58
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:14,519
I'm not going.

59
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,360
Hear me out first.

60
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:18,399
This show is extremely flexible.

61
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:19,439
Hardly any cameras in sight,

62
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,560
no script restrictions.

63
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,000
I'm not going.

64
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,160
Don't be stubborn.

65
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:27,439
Xingyu has already pulled
all your resources.

66
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,319
Everyone's saying you're being blacklisted.

67
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,359
This show is by an independent team,

68
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,360
no company channels.

69
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,896
The entertainment industry
is never short of new faces.

70
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,480
If you keep dragging this out,

71
00:05:35,481 --> 00:05:36,920
the audience will forget your name.

72
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,800
I'm not going.

73
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,720
Just a work call.

74
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:53,839
I know.

75
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,560
Do I look that petty to you?

76
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,759
But I think Sister Si Han has a point.

77
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,720
It's a really good opportunity.

78
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,040
You want me to go too?

79
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:07,759
Mm-hmm.

80
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:09,879
But I'm a top star.

81
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:11,439
A countryside show...

82
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,959
sounds miserable.

83
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:14,759
I don't want to go.

84
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,800
But...

85
00:06:16,879 --> 00:06:17,560
Wen Nuannuan!

86
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,600
I know you're home!

87
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,800
Open up!

88
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,360
It's Auntie.

89
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,040
What's Auntie doing here?

90
00:06:26,079 --> 00:06:27,160
She's here for money.

91
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,920
After my parents passed away,

92
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,360
my uncle and aunt raised me.

93
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:33,879
You know that.

94
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,480
I know.

95
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,879
But they haven't treated you well.

96
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:40,119
They took your parents' compensation money,

97
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,560
and seized your family's house.

98
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:44,399
You don't owe them anything.

99
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,480
Actually...

100
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,600
there's something else I haven't told you.

101
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,600
Back then...

102
00:06:52,162 --> 00:06:53,560
it was my aunt who stopped me...

103
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:55,199
from going to find you.

104
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,240
Where are you going?

105
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:07,680
Auntie.

106
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,279
I've already made the food.

107
00:07:09,713 --> 00:07:11,920
I have something urgent
to deal with, I have to go out.

108
00:07:12,959 --> 00:07:14,399
Going to find that Xiao He, are you?

109
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,576
Everyone knows about
your disgusting little affair.

110
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,600
How shameless are you?

111
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:18,279
What,

112
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,600
still have the nerve...

113
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:20,759
to go see her?

114
00:07:21,079 --> 00:07:21,639
Auntie,

115
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,920
she's leaving today.

116
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,160
I have to see her.

117
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:27,120
That indecent creature!

118
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,160
Good riddance.

119
00:07:28,519 --> 00:07:28,920
Let me tell you,

120
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,239
you're not going anywhere.

121
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,040
Our family...

122
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,320
can't afford the disgrace.

123
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,920
You being rotten is one thing,

124
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:34,759
but...

125
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,160
I won't let you affect your cousin.

126
00:07:37,279 --> 00:07:38,279
Stay right here.

127
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,576
You're not going anywhere.

128
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,600
Auntie!

129
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,160
Auntie!

130
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,560
Auntie, open the door!

131
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,640
By the time I smashed the window...

132
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,120
and rushed to the hospital,

133
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,639
you were already gone.

134
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,920
So...

135
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,519
you didn't mean to abandon me.

136
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,000
Right.

137
00:08:10,439 --> 00:08:11,560
There's one more thing...

138
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:12,959
I never told you.

139
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:14,839
Actually...

140
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,399
it doesn't matter anymore, Nuannuan.

141
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,720
As long as you're with
me now, that's enough.

142
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:20,439
Okay.

143
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,720
Nuannuan.

144
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,439
Nuannuan!

145
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,079
Quick, quick, quick!

146
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,399
Come with Auntie!

147
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,040
Come with me, come on!

148
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:32,000
Auntie's found you a great catch!

149
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,120
He has a house, a car,

150
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:33,759
a stable job.

151
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,080
Auntie,

152
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,039
what are you doing?

153
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:35,759
I'm not going!

154
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,000
If you don't get married,

155
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:39,639
how will your cousin
afford the bride price?

156
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:40,399
Listen to me:

157
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,320
Either get married,

158
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,600
or cough up the money.

159
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:44,096
I haven't even started the job yet.

160
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,200
Where would I get a salary?

161
00:08:45,559 --> 00:08:46,559
No salary, huh?

162
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:50,240
Yet you can afford to
rent back your old place?

163
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,720
Playing poor with me?

164
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,159
I've heard all about it.

165
00:08:54,879 --> 00:08:56,759
You're assistant to some big star.

166
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,639
A month's pay...

167
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,960
five figures!

168
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:03,120
And the motorcycle parked in the yard...

169
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,000
is that the big star's ride?

170
00:09:06,632 --> 00:09:07,632
Don't touch that!

171
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:08,960
Fine, don't go.

172
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,200
Just give this motorbike...

173
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,240
to your cousin.

174
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:12,679
Why should I?!

175
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:15,559
On what basis would she give that to him?

176
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:18,240
And who do you think you are?

177
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:20,639
I'm her boss.

178
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:27,840
So you're that big star, Lin Can?

179
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,440
Ran into a celebrity here!

180
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,000
Let me get a picture!

181
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,336
Don't you dare take pictures!

182
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:36,639
Get back!

183
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:37,240
No pictures!

184
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:37,720
What's wrong with taking a picture?

185
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,200
This is my house!

186
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:38,879
You can't just snap photos!

187
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:39,759
Get away!

188
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:40,759
Move!

189
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:42,319
What's the big deal about a picture?

190
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,759
Met a celebrity!

191
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:46,959
Why are you blocking my shot?

192
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,960
Why are you filming me?

193
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:50,399
Let the whole country see...

194
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,080
an aunt forcing her niece...

195
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,640
to pay for her son's bride price.

196
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,720
With my following,

197
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,120
that should trend, right?

198
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:59,279
Hmph!

199
00:09:59,919 --> 00:10:00,959
Let me tell you something,

200
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,200
Nuannuan...

201
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,920
has been raised by us...

202
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,279
since she was little.

203
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,440
Clothes to wear,

204
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:07,200
clothes to buy,

205
00:10:07,279 --> 00:10:08,080
university...

206
00:10:08,279 --> 00:10:09,440
we paid for it all!

207
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,879
So what's wrong...

208
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,375
with her helping her cousin...

209
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,559
with the bride price?

210
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,840
Huh?

211
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,360
But...

212
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,399
you look...

213
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,399
familiar.

214
00:10:22,519 --> 00:10:22,679
What?

215
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:27,480
Let's talk about where her parents'
compensation money went first.

216
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:28,120
You... you... you...

217
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,360
You!

218
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,840
Now I remember!

219
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:37,039
You...

220
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:39,360
you're that Xiao He from back then!

221
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:45,679
No wonder!

222
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,000
Even back then,

223
00:10:47,193 --> 00:10:49,073
you two were up to that disgusting stuff.

224
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,480
And now...

225
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,960
sure enough,

226
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,480
you're back together.

227
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,120
But that's fine too.

228
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,440
You're rich now, right?

229
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,120
I guess you could say...

230
00:10:58,159 --> 00:11:00,120
our Nuannuan is marrying up.

231
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,440
So Nuannuan's brother...

232
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:03,679
is your brother too.

233
00:11:04,519 --> 00:11:07,200
Helping your brother
with the bride price...

234
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:08,919
isn't too much to ask, is it?

235
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,200
Why should she pay?!

236
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:11,960
Go.

237
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:12,799
What are you doing?

238
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:13,840
Who do you think you are?!

239
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,120
Get out!

240
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,120
The internet says
you're getting blacklisted.

241
00:11:15,121 --> 00:11:16,135
Better scram while you can!

242
00:11:16,159 --> 00:11:17,919
Let's see how much
longer you can act tough!

243
00:11:18,399 --> 00:11:19,039
Open the door!

244
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,519
Open the door, I said!

245
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,080
Come out here if you dare!

246
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:25,039
It's okay.

247
00:11:26,399 --> 00:11:27,000
How about...

248
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,080
we go for a ride?

249
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:46,159
Eat up.

250
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:57,759
Feeling better?

251
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,080
Much better.

252
00:12:01,559 --> 00:12:02,719
It feels like the troubles...

253
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:03,799
are slowly fading.

254
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:06,600
Don't worry about your aunt.

255
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:07,919
I'll help you handle it.

256
00:12:08,759 --> 00:12:09,759
It's fine.

257
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:10,720
It's my problem.

258
00:12:10,721 --> 00:12:11,759
I'll solve it myself.

259
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:13,679
Consider it...

260
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:15,119
rent for staying at your place.

261
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,240
Do you...

262
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:21,080
want to go to the countryside with me?

263
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:24,759
You mean...

264
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,399
you're taking that show?

265
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:27,480
Mm-hmm.

266
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:30,039
I can't stay down forever.

267
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,200
Whatever you do,

268
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,799
I'll be with you.

269
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,440
Changed my mind.

270
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:12,399
I'll go.

271
00:13:12,879 --> 00:13:13,200
Good.

272
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,440
I'll make the arrangements.

273
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:18,399
Finally wrapped.

274
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,000
I'm exhausted.

275
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,320
No more smoking.

276
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:26,600
I don't want to smell it.

277
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,000
All these years,

278
00:13:31,001 --> 00:13:32,241
you never changed your perfume.

279
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,279
I knew it.

280
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,440
My old self...

281
00:13:35,441 --> 00:13:36,720
still stirs something in you.

282
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,799
Don't flatter yourself.

283
00:13:39,799 --> 00:13:40,799
Si Han.

284
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,639
You're by my side again.

285
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:44,559
It's so good.

286
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:48,559
Hurry up and get in.

287
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:01,600
Smells amazing.

288
00:14:04,559 --> 00:14:05,559
Si Han.

289
00:14:06,879 --> 00:14:08,360
It's so good...

290
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,000
to have you with me.

291
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:14,120
I'll always be with you.

292
00:14:25,279 --> 00:14:26,279
Si Han.

293
00:14:27,279 --> 00:14:29,200
Let's raise a rabbit together, okay?

294
00:14:30,799 --> 00:14:31,799
Mm.

295
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,720
Miss Jiang,

296
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,000
mind the setting.

297
00:14:46,559 --> 00:14:47,559
What if I don't?

298
00:14:49,759 --> 00:14:50,759
Si Han.

299
00:14:51,399 --> 00:14:52,559
Let's start over.

300
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:54,960
Like last night.

301
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,320
Sit properly.

302
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,679
You clearly can't let me go.

303
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:37,720
Sit properly.

304
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:47,440
Lin Can can join that variety show.

305
00:15:48,279 --> 00:15:49,279
But...

306
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,240
I'm going too.

307
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:55,080
A lady of your status, Miss Jiang,

308
00:15:55,679 --> 00:15:56,679
there's no need.

309
00:15:57,639 --> 00:15:58,639
Two choices.

310
00:15:59,039 --> 00:16:00,039
One:

311
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,080
You go with me.

312
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:01,960
Two:

313
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,559
No one goes.

314
00:16:19,799 --> 00:16:21,399
It's only three days.

315
00:16:21,559 --> 00:16:23,039
Do you need to bring this much?

316
00:16:24,679 --> 00:16:25,679
What should I do?

317
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,280
I can't possibly pack everything.

318
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:29,720
Need sunscreen.

319
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,120
My facial repair cream has to come too.

320
00:16:39,159 --> 00:16:40,159
This power bank...

321
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,480
do we need three?

322
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:43,960
Alright.

323
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:46,120
There might be no signal there anyway.

324
00:16:47,919 --> 00:16:48,919
I'll bring one for you.

325
00:16:49,399 --> 00:16:50,919
But I'm taking my helmet.

326
00:16:51,559 --> 00:16:52,959
They might have some...

327
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,559
motorcycle shooting or something.

328
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:01,039
I heard from the crew...

329
00:17:01,759 --> 00:17:03,240
there's a field work segment.

330
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:05,799
These high heels might...

331
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,799
sink into the mud.

332
00:17:10,519 --> 00:17:11,519
And these sunglasses...

333
00:17:13,032 --> 00:17:14,153
These sunglasses...

334
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:15,399
do we need three pairs?

335
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:18,759
Then you...

336
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:19,920
take them out.

337
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,079
I need to bring my autograph pen.

338
00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:26,759
What if they recognize me...

339
00:17:27,279 --> 00:17:28,720
and swarm me for signatures?

340
00:17:30,119 --> 00:17:31,400
The troubles of being a star.

341
00:17:33,839 --> 00:17:34,960
Go.

342
00:17:39,404 --> 00:17:40,404
Go.

343
00:17:43,359 --> 00:17:44,359
Fine.

344
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,640
Bring this.

345
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,200
Alright.

346
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,400
Come on out.

347
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:47,839
Nuannuan.

348
00:18:48,365 --> 00:18:48,886
Cover for me.

349
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:49,759
What's for lunch today?

350
00:18:49,760 --> 00:18:51,318
That uncle still has a flip phone.

351
00:18:51,319 --> 00:18:51,799
Almost home.

352
00:18:51,799 --> 00:18:52,799
Um...

353
00:18:53,119 --> 00:18:53,559
Uncle,

354
00:18:53,839 --> 00:18:54,839
do you know her?

355
00:18:57,759 --> 00:18:58,240
Nope.

356
00:18:58,319 --> 00:18:59,559
You folks from another village?

357
00:19:00,119 --> 00:19:01,119
Uncle,

358
00:19:01,160 --> 00:19:02,839
this is a big star!

359
00:19:03,039 --> 00:19:04,039
Lin Can.

360
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,640
What big star?

361
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:07,680
Who's a big star?

362
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:08,400
Never mind.

363
00:19:08,559 --> 00:19:09,599
Go have your lunch, uncle.

364
00:19:11,079 --> 00:19:11,799
Well,

365
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:13,640
the sunglasses were pointless.

366
00:19:14,519 --> 00:19:15,815
This place probably has no internet.

367
00:19:15,839 --> 00:19:17,000
They don't even know me.

368
00:19:20,359 --> 00:19:21,518
We've been here a while.

369
00:19:21,519 --> 00:19:23,359
Haven't seen a single crew member.

370
00:19:24,559 --> 00:19:26,199
Guess it's true, like Sister Si Han said.

371
00:19:26,759 --> 00:19:27,880
This show...

372
00:19:28,279 --> 00:19:29,319
is extremely free-form.

373
00:19:34,119 --> 00:19:35,759
Maybe this place isn't so bad after all.

374
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:39,359
I'm starting to look
forward to the days ahead.

375
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,640
Wait for me!

376
00:19:52,079 --> 00:19:53,079
Jiang Wan.

377
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,200
What are you doing here?

378
00:19:56,559 --> 00:19:58,279
If it isn't our top star.

379
00:20:00,043 --> 00:20:01,043
I forgot,

380
00:20:01,279 --> 00:20:03,079
you're washed up now.

381
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:06,680
Si Han.

382
00:20:07,079 --> 00:20:08,079
What's going on?

383
00:20:10,039 --> 00:20:11,039
She's... an accident.

384
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:11,640
Don't mind her.

385
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:12,640
Focus on the shoot.

386
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:15,000
Who's an accident?

387
00:20:15,359 --> 00:20:16,359
Explain yourself!

388
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:17,960
I won't be with her.

389
00:20:18,359 --> 00:20:19,359
Let's go.

390
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:20,000
Lin Can.

391
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,000
Don't be rash.

392
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:22,735
She's here on purpose to cause trouble.

393
00:20:22,759 --> 00:20:23,839
If you leave, she wins.

394
00:20:24,440 --> 00:20:25,440
Exactly.

395
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:27,759
Don't be so tense.

396
00:20:29,079 --> 00:20:30,079
What,

397
00:20:30,319 --> 00:20:31,400
scared of me now?

398
00:20:31,759 --> 00:20:32,759
Me? Scared of you?

399
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:33,920
You wish.

400
00:20:35,799 --> 00:20:36,799
You stay right there!

401
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:37,880
Are you crazy?

402
00:20:38,759 --> 00:20:40,078
I haven't seen you in
days, itching for a beating?

403
00:20:40,079 --> 00:20:41,039
Alright, alright, alright!

404
00:20:41,039 --> 00:20:41,759
Calm down.

405
00:20:41,839 --> 00:20:42,359
Take it easy, easy.

406
00:20:42,360 --> 00:20:44,039
Si Han, look at her!

407
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:47,799
Can you two quiet down?

408
00:20:48,279 --> 00:20:49,399
Why do you fight the moment you meet?

409
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,640
Every single time.

410
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:53,880
What kind of dump is this?

411
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:55,920
Lin Can,

412
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,240
this is all your fault!

413
00:20:58,359 --> 00:20:59,359
Little assistant.

414
00:20:59,759 --> 00:21:00,759
Tell me,

415
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:02,000
what are they talking about?

416
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:06,559
Sorry, Teacher Jiang Wan.

417
00:21:07,799 --> 00:21:08,799
So clumsy.

418
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:10,680
I don't know what Lin Can sees in you.

419
00:21:11,319 --> 00:21:12,079
Yeah.

420
00:21:12,319 --> 00:21:13,519
I'm clumsy.

421
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:17,319
Sister Si Han and Lin
Can are a better match.

422
00:21:18,559 --> 00:21:19,000
No,

423
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:20,480
that's not what I meant.

424
00:21:21,559 --> 00:21:23,359
How can you give up so easily?

425
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:26,200
If you want something, fight for it!

426
00:21:27,519 --> 00:21:28,519
Teacher Jiang Wan...

427
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,599
do you like Sister Si Han?

428
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,000
You can tell?

429
00:21:35,759 --> 00:21:37,599
The look in your eyes
when you like someone...

430
00:21:38,039 --> 00:21:39,039
is impossible to hide.

431
00:21:40,039 --> 00:21:41,039
Is that so?

432
00:21:41,599 --> 00:21:42,599
Then tell me,

433
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,520
what kind of look does Si Han give me?

434
00:21:49,039 --> 00:21:50,680
A murderous look.

435
00:21:51,279 --> 00:21:52,279
Nonsense!

436
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:53,200
Idiot.

437
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:54,760
Talking to you is pointless.

438
00:21:55,359 --> 00:21:56,439
You don't need to say more.

439
00:21:56,559 --> 00:21:57,639
I won't stay if she's here.

440
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,319
You have to stay.

441
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:02,280
It's your last chance to make a comeback.

442
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:03,039
It's fine.

443
00:22:03,279 --> 00:22:03,680
Doesn't matter.

444
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,880
I've already found the
most important thing.

445
00:22:07,119 --> 00:22:08,640
But what if Nuannuan wants to stay?

446
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:17,799
How are they still not done?

447
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:20,119
Go listen to what they're saying.

448
00:22:20,559 --> 00:22:22,359
Eavesdropping isn't nice.

449
00:22:24,119 --> 00:22:25,119
You...

450
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:26,400
seem smart enough,

451
00:22:27,559 --> 00:22:28,599
but you're such a goose.

452
00:22:30,119 --> 00:22:31,240
I'm not going.

453
00:22:33,153 --> 00:22:34,353
How much does Lin Can pay you?

454
00:22:34,559 --> 00:22:35,559
I'll double it.

455
00:22:36,079 --> 00:22:37,079
No, no, no.

456
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,200
Triple!

457
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:40,240
Well...

458
00:22:42,119 --> 00:22:42,680
That...

459
00:22:43,079 --> 00:22:43,519
Jiang Wan.

460
00:22:43,799 --> 00:22:45,079
Hands off her.

461
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:47,880
Si Han...

462
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:50,159
My poor feet hurt so much...

463
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:50,559
Fine.

464
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,000
I'll have someone drive you home.

465
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:53,480
No, no, no!

466
00:22:53,759 --> 00:22:54,759
I'm not leaving!

467
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:55,920
I won't go!

468
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:57,960
Nuannuan.

469
00:22:58,359 --> 00:22:59,359
Sister Si Han, go ahead.

470
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:01,440
Look me in the eye and tell me:

471
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:02,720
Do you like it here?

472
00:23:04,559 --> 00:23:05,920
I think it's nice.

473
00:23:06,119 --> 00:23:07,119
Free and easy.

474
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,440
See?

475
00:23:11,279 --> 00:23:12,279
Alright, alright.

476
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:14,319
But I won't do tasks with her.

477
00:23:14,519 --> 00:23:15,920
Like I want to see you!

478
00:23:18,599 --> 00:23:19,599
Lin Can.

479
00:23:28,559 --> 00:23:29,559
Come quick!

480
00:23:33,559 --> 00:23:34,799
What a cozy room.

481
00:23:37,799 --> 00:23:38,400
Not bad.

482
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:39,640
Livable.

483
00:23:46,079 --> 00:23:47,279
Hello, girls!

484
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:50,160
Hello.

485
00:23:50,161 --> 00:23:51,720
I'm the owner of this homestay.

486
00:23:51,839 --> 00:23:53,079
Just call me Sister Ling.

487
00:23:53,359 --> 00:23:53,640
Here,

488
00:23:53,641 --> 00:23:55,559
homemade rice wine
from our mountain spring.

489
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:56,240
It's delicious.

490
00:23:56,359 --> 00:23:57,359
Have a taste.

491
00:24:01,559 --> 00:24:02,679
Do you have sparkling water?

492
00:24:03,559 --> 00:24:04,559
Afraid not.

493
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:06,440
This is famous mountain spring water.

494
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:08,160
Many people come just for it.

495
00:24:10,119 --> 00:24:11,160
Thank you, Sister Ling.

496
00:24:11,519 --> 00:24:11,920
No trouble.

497
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,160
If you need anything,

498
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,160
just come find me.

499
00:24:14,319 --> 00:24:14,559
Oh,

500
00:24:14,759 --> 00:24:16,519
remember to change into slippers later.

501
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,279
Is there a schedule?

502
00:24:19,599 --> 00:24:20,599
You'll know soon enough.

503
00:24:21,839 --> 00:24:22,919
Don't worry, get some rest.

504
00:24:23,039 --> 00:24:24,039
Thanks, Sister Ling.

505
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:31,720
I'm regretting coming here.

506
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:33,799
Everything else is fine,

507
00:24:34,759 --> 00:24:36,279
I just can't stand seeing Jiang Wan.

508
00:24:37,119 --> 00:24:38,720
But I think it's nice.

509
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:40,400
What's nice?

510
00:24:43,319 --> 00:24:44,359
Here,

511
00:24:45,519 --> 00:24:46,519
it's just...

512
00:24:46,599 --> 00:24:47,599
the two of us.

513
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,240
We...

514
00:24:49,319 --> 00:24:50,319
are on our own.

515
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:01,599
Girls!

516
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:02,680
Dinnertime!

517
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:04,920
Coming!

518
00:25:05,079 --> 00:25:06,119
I'll change into slippers.

519
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,480
I'm so hungry.

520
00:25:15,799 --> 00:25:16,359
Sister Ling,

521
00:25:16,759 --> 00:25:17,880
can we eat first?

522
00:25:18,119 --> 00:25:20,200
Can't we do the boat task after dinner?

523
00:25:21,319 --> 00:25:22,319
Can't help it.

524
00:25:22,559 --> 00:25:24,680
This is a task the crew
specifically gave me.

525
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:27,240
But whoever wins the race first...

526
00:25:27,519 --> 00:25:29,519
gets a barbecue feast tonight!

527
00:25:30,359 --> 00:25:31,359
Barbecue feast!

528
00:25:32,319 --> 00:25:32,880
Is this water...

529
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,119
clean?

530
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,640
My immune system is weak.

531
00:25:36,119 --> 00:25:37,119
I don't want to compete.

532
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:38,799
If you're scared, don't compete.

533
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,440
Just forfeit.

534
00:25:42,240 --> 00:25:42,880
Fine, we'll compete!

535
00:25:43,119 --> 00:25:44,119
Who's afraid of who?

536
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:48,039
Then you'll form teams for the race.

537
00:25:48,519 --> 00:25:49,519
Good luck!

538
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:51,760
We'll definitely beat them!

539
00:25:53,559 --> 00:25:54,559
I believe in you.

540
00:25:58,359 --> 00:25:59,160
We're a team.

541
00:25:59,279 --> 00:26:00,279
Pick the blue one.

542
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,119
Don't splash me!

543
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:14,000
Pass them!

544
00:26:14,200 --> 00:26:15,200
I can do it!

545
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:16,759
Faster, faster!

546
00:26:16,760 --> 00:26:18,279
It's okay, we can pass them!

547
00:26:21,599 --> 00:26:21,960
One!

548
00:26:22,119 --> 00:26:22,519
Two!

549
00:26:22,759 --> 00:26:23,079
Go!

550
00:26:23,079 --> 00:26:23,279
One!

551
00:26:23,279 --> 00:26:23,599
Two!

552
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:24,160
Pass them!

553
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:24,440
One!

554
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:25,440
Two!

555
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:26,599
Go!

556
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:28,039
We have to pass them!

557
00:26:28,599 --> 00:26:29,720
Pass them!

558
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:40,599
Lin Can!

559
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:42,319
You cheated!

560
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,640
We won!

561
00:26:44,039 --> 00:26:45,839
Let's race back!

562
00:26:47,279 --> 00:26:48,559
You're learning to cheat too?

563
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:50,040
You'll lose going back too!

564
00:26:50,839 --> 00:26:51,279
Go!

565
00:26:51,279 --> 00:26:52,279
Yeah!

566
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:02,480
You're amazing.

567
00:27:04,559 --> 00:27:05,559
We won!

568
00:27:06,119 --> 00:27:07,119
We won!

569
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:14,880
Get up here!

570
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:15,880
Silly!

571
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:27,200
(Easter egg)

572
00:27:40,222 --> 00:27:43,120
I really thought
you weren't going to come.

573
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,680
Too bad.

574
00:27:46,039 --> 00:27:47,039
Lin Can already left.

575
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:51,880
Nuannuan.

576
00:27:52,119 --> 00:27:53,439
Lin Can has her own life to live.

577
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:55,400
Being apart...

578
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,800
might be for the best for both of you.

579
00:27:58,599 --> 00:27:59,599
Shen Hao.

580
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:01,160
Don't you pretend to care here.

581
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:03,160
If you hadn't told my aunt,

582
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:04,920
we wouldn't have been torn apart.

583
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:09,839
What are you looking at?

584
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:11,160
Not embarrassed enough?

585
00:28:11,519 --> 00:28:12,519
Get your butt home now!

586
00:28:13,119 --> 00:28:13,759
Enough.

587
00:28:13,759 --> 00:28:14,759
Let's go.

588
00:28:15,039 --> 00:28:15,839
Move it!

589
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,000
Disgrace!

590
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,640
Rich people are so easy.

591
00:28:22,079 --> 00:28:23,399
If they say they'll
pay, they pay.

592
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,000
